# soffice

- docx to pdf

```sh
curl -L -m 120 "http://localhost:8022/api/v1/convert_data/" -H "x-cellosign-request-id: testing-testing-123123" -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d "{
    \"document\": \"\",
    \"document_type\": \"docx\"
}";
```

- xlsx to html

```sh
curl -L -m 120 "http://localhost:8022/api/v1/convert_data/" -H "x-cellosign-request-id: testing-testing-123123" -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d "{
    \"document\": \"\",
    \"document_type\": \"xlsx\"
}";
```
